1136
01:44:07,463 --> 01:44:09,831
<i>Acercándose...</i>

1137
01:44:09,832 --> 01:44:11,366
<i>...cada vez más...</i>

1138
01:44:11,367 --> 01:44:15,703
...al momento inarticulado...

1139
01:44:15,704 --> 01:44:17,405
...del comienzo.

1140
01:44:27,616 --> 01:44:30,051
<i>¿Pero a qué costo?</i>

1141
01:44:32,354 --> 01:44:33,621
<i>Madam no está sufriendo...</i>

1142
01:44:33,622 --> 01:44:35,723
